This,API,is,a,Security,Assertion,Markup,Language,SAML,standard,for,logging,users,into,applications,based,on,their,sessions,in,another,context,This,single,sign,on,SSO,login,standard,has,advantages,over,logging,in,using,a,username,password,by,OneLogin,is,an,Identity,and,Access,Management,IAM,provider,for,enterprise,in,cloud,legacy,and,hybrid,IT,environments